                <h2>
                  <p>A field of intellectual research</p>
                </h2>
              </div>
            
            
            
            
            
           

        

      
    
    

                 
          

          
          
            
            
            
                <div class="cover js-splash-cover" data-splash-type="image" data-splash-image-url="/img/oiGBvYQhWgmAmT_GwqStRCyG-co=/1920x1080/9604/8640/DR2004_0136_016.jpg"></div>
                <div class="caption ">
                  
                    <p>Cedric Price and Frank Newby&rsquo;s research project Lightweight Enclosures Unit is one of twenty-three case studies in <i>The Other Architect</i>, now on tour in Buenos Aires and New York.</br>
CCA DR2004:0136:016</p>
                  
